WEBVTT

00:00:27.470 --> 00:00:28.150 line:80%
Wait.

00:00:30.510 --> 00:00:31.310 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:00:32.150 --> 00:00:33.880 line:80%
This medicine is a bit numbing.

00:00:36.150 --> 00:00:36.950 line:80%
Bear with it.

00:00:46.910 --> 00:00:48.710 line:80%
Didn't you say you were leaving?

00:00:49.470 --> 00:00:52.000 line:80%
I've been preparing some things for you.

00:00:54.550 --> 00:00:56.470 line:80%
There are clothes, shoes,

00:00:57.040 --> 00:00:58.040 line:80%
and bank notes.

00:00:59.640 --> 00:01:02.150 line:80%
It will be easier for you to carry them.

00:01:03.400 --> 00:01:04.460 line:80%
And the divorce...

00:01:09.589 --> 00:01:10.920 line:80%
And the divorce papers.

00:01:12.480 --> 00:01:14.280 line:80%
It just needs your fingerprint.

00:01:16.580 --> 00:01:19.040 line:80%
You've really thought of everything
for me.

00:01:23.110 --> 00:01:24.510 line:80%
Now that you're leaving,

00:01:25.110 --> 00:01:27.480 line:80%
we should have some closure between us.

00:01:28.480 --> 00:01:30.280 line:80%
It'll make things easier for you

00:01:30.480 --> 00:01:31.670 line:80%
in the future.

00:01:34.110 --> 00:01:35.910 line:80%
You don't need to worry about me.

00:01:38.080 --> 00:01:38.940 line:80%
What about you?

00:01:39.870 --> 00:01:41.800 line:80%
What are your plans for the future?

00:01:43.480 --> 00:01:44.750 line:80%
I told you before.

00:01:45.750 --> 00:01:47.279 line:80%
If Lin'an stays peaceful,

00:01:48.110 --> 00:01:49.279 line:80%
I'll run a pig farm—

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:53.230 line:80%
buying, butchering, and selling pigs.

00:01:56.670 --> 00:01:57.750 line:80%
What I'm asking is,

00:01:59.870 --> 00:02:01.200 line:80%
if I really leave,

00:02:02.720 --> 00:02:04.080 line:80%
will you marry someone

00:02:04.670 --> 00:02:06.730 line:80%
or have another matrilocal husband?

00:02:11.710 --> 00:02:14.910 line:80%
Marrying someone
or having another matrilocal husband?

00:02:17.710 --> 00:02:19.310 line:80%
I'll think about that later.

00:02:19.430 --> 00:02:20.800 line:80%
Life has to go on.

00:02:31.670 --> 00:02:32.320 line:80%
Fine.

00:02:36.600 --> 00:02:39.080 line:80%
Remember to tell me
what kind of man you like.

00:02:40.480 --> 00:02:42.640 line:80%
I'll keep an eye out for you.

00:02:51.430 --> 00:02:53.830 line:80%
Definitely not someone cold and stubborn.

00:02:56.270 --> 00:02:57.670 line:80%
You have such a sharp tongue.

00:02:57.670 --> 00:02:59.040 line:80%
You should worry first about

00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:01.100 line:80%
whether you can find yourself a wife.

00:03:05.760 --> 00:03:07.110 line:80%
Don't worry about me.

00:03:07.430 --> 00:03:09.760 line:80%
If I do marry,
it won't be someone like you.

00:03:10.550 --> 00:03:14.680 line:80%
At least I'll find someone who's gentle
and knows how to take care of a home.

00:03:16.920 --> 00:03:17.640 line:80%
Right.

00:03:17.950 --> 00:03:20.010 line:80%
Well, I've always preferred someone

00:03:20.160 --> 00:03:22.620 line:80%
refined, well-read,
and who loves to smile.

00:03:36.710 --> 00:03:38.240 line:80%
Anyway, we've been through

00:03:38.800 --> 00:03:40.270 line:80%
so much together.

00:03:43.080 --> 00:03:45.810 line:80%
So just wish me luck
in finding a refined husband.

00:03:51.990 --> 00:03:52.640 line:80%
Alright.

00:03:54.040 --> 00:03:55.570 line:80%
I hope your wish comes true.

00:04:00.480 --> 00:04:01.410 line:80%
I'm leaving now.

00:04:18.990 --> 00:04:20.319 line:80%
Have you lost your mind?

00:04:22.070 --> 00:04:23.360 line:80%
You feel that wronged?

00:04:24.040 --> 00:04:25.310 line:80%
You're leaving anyway.

00:04:25.310 --> 00:04:26.510 line:80%
Why did you harass me?

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:27.600 line:80%
Harass you?

00:04:28.630 --> 00:04:30.430 line:80%
If I really wanted to harass you,

00:04:31.070 --> 00:04:33.070 line:80%
I wouldn't have waited until today!

00:04:33.670 --> 00:04:35.930 line:80%
You really like pedantic scholars, huh?

00:04:36.360 --> 00:04:38.959 line:80%
You just want someone like Song Yan,
don't you?

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:41.360 line:80%
♪ In this life ♪

00:04:41.380 --> 00:04:43.510 line:80%
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

00:04:43.540 --> 00:04:45.430 line:80%
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

00:04:46.030 --> 00:04:46.880 line:80%
♪ On this journey ♪

00:04:46.910 --> 00:04:49.700 line:80%
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:51.770 line:80%
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:52.440 line:80%
♪ After we part  ♪

00:04:52.459 --> 00:04:55.420 line:80%
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

00:04:55.440 --> 00:04:57.770 line:80%
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

00:04:57.800 --> 00:05:02.710 line:80%
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

00:05:03.030 --> 00:05:03.850 line:80%
♪ In this life ♪

00:05:03.870 --> 00:05:06.290 line:80%
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

00:05:06.310 --> 00:05:08.380 line:80%
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

00:05:08.750 --> 00:05:09.670 line:80%
♪ On this journey ♪

00:05:09.690 --> 00:05:12.460 line:80%
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

00:05:12.480 --> 00:05:14.400 line:80%
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

00:05:14.430 --> 00:05:15.370 line:80%
♪ After we part  ♪

00:05:15.400 --> 00:05:18.140 line:80%
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

00:05:18.210 --> 00:05:20.580 line:80%
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

00:05:20.610 --> 00:05:25.440 line:80%
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:22.370 line:80%
Who do you think you are,

00:05:22.600 --> 00:05:23.670 line:80%
leaving whenever you want

00:05:23.670 --> 00:05:25.930 line:80%
and kissing me whenever you feel like it?

00:05:26.060 --> 00:05:30.180 line:80%
♪ We'll never be apart ♪

00:05:35.800 --> 00:05:36.550 line:80%
Do it.

00:05:43.110 --> 00:05:44.750 line:80%
You have bad taste in men.

00:05:45.959 --> 00:05:48.020 line:80%
Instead of ending up with an ingrate,

00:05:48.430 --> 00:05:49.760 line:80%
why not come with me now?

00:06:03.960 --> 00:06:06.160 line:80%
I do have bad taste in men.

00:06:07.550 --> 00:06:08.870 line:80%
That's why I saved you.

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:12.190 line:80%
I have an enemy.

00:06:14.920 --> 00:06:15.870 line:80%
Either he dies,

00:06:17.110 --> 00:06:18.190 line:80%
or I do.

00:06:31.670 --> 00:06:33.090 line:80%
Just wait a year for me.

00:06:34.670 --> 00:06:35.670 line:80%
If I die,

00:06:37.310 --> 00:06:38.770 line:80%
someone will write to you.

00:06:39.280 --> 00:06:40.880 line:80%
-Then you can marry ag—
-Why?

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:44.750 line:80%
You keep saying Song Yan is an ingrate.

00:06:44.750 --> 00:06:45.810 line:80%
But what about you?

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:48.959 line:80%
You harassed me,

00:06:50.550 --> 00:06:52.680 line:80%
then you said you have feelings for me.

00:06:54.230 --> 00:06:55.630 line:80%
Why should I wait for you?

00:06:58.870 --> 00:06:59.750 line:80%
Why?

00:07:01.910 --> 00:07:03.550 line:80%
♪ I just don't want to ♪

00:07:04.170 --> 00:07:05.020 line:80%
♪ Keep weighing every word ♪

00:07:05.040 --> 00:07:07.210 line:80%
♪ And hiding in time in silence ♪

00:07:08.220 --> 00:07:09.960 line:80%
♪ It's not that I don't believe in karma ♪

00:07:10.620 --> 00:07:12.780 line:80%
♪ That I'm being stubborn ♪

00:07:14.840 --> 00:07:16.290 line:80%
♪ Some endings have long been ♪

00:07:17.250 --> 00:07:18.520 line:80%
♪ Weathered through a thousand years ♪

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:20.550 line:80%
♪ Traced by those who come after ♪

00:07:21.140 --> 00:07:22.910 line:80%
♪ Compared to fading away in sorrow ♪

00:07:23.590 --> 00:07:25.480 line:80%
♪ I'd rather fight ♪

00:07:26.610 --> 00:07:29.170 line:80%
♪ Life's bitterness ♪

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:32.080 line:80%
♪ Comes from love ♪

00:07:32.790 --> 00:07:35.380 line:80%
♪ Love, yet so hard to hold ♪

00:07:36.030 --> 00:07:38.680 line:80%
♪ Like holing a torch in the wilderness ♪

00:07:39.470 --> 00:07:41.630 line:80%
♪ Time sings a mournful song ♪

00:07:42.340 --> 00:07:44.390 line:80%
♪ Gathered little yet parted often ♪

00:07:44.959 --> 00:07:46.360 line:80%
You save me here,

00:07:45.330 --> 00:07:48.230 line:80%
♪ Just as tears fall into the long river ♪

00:07:48.280 --> 00:07:49.800 line:80%
and abandoned me here.

00:07:48.980 --> 00:07:54.430 line:80%
♪ I must dive into the starry stream ♪

00:07:51.480 --> 00:07:55.160 line:80%
I suppose... things have come full circle.

00:09:35.010 --> 00:09:40.480 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:09:40.570 --> 00:09:43.250 line:80%
[Episode 17]

00:11:32.890 --> 00:11:40.370 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:11:48.950 --> 00:11:51.150 line:80%
Yan Zheng barely spoke when he was home,

00:11:54.070 --> 00:11:55.600 line:80%
but why does it feel so quiet

00:11:59.040 --> 00:12:00.240 line:80%
now that he's gone?

00:12:42.310 --> 00:12:43.880 line:80%
Happy birthday.

00:12:44.310 --> 00:12:46.510 line:80%
May you be forever joyful and carefree.

00:12:47.120 --> 00:12:49.000 line:80%
He always uses such simple words.

00:12:49.920 --> 00:12:51.590 line:80%
Does he think I couldn't read?

00:12:51.860 --> 00:12:53.660 line:80%
[Happy birthday.
May you be forever joyful and carefree.]

00:13:35.920 --> 00:13:37.430 line:80%
What's wrong with your wrist?

00:13:37.430 --> 00:13:40.120 line:80%
The ox cart tipped over
when I was collecting pigs yesterday.

00:13:40.120 --> 00:13:41.780 line:80%
I used my hand to break the fall

00:13:41.920 --> 00:13:42.850 line:80%
and sprained it.

00:13:42.950 --> 00:13:44.950 line:80%
Changyu's wrist hurts often.

00:13:45.190 --> 00:13:47.000 line:80%
Butchering pigs is tiring work.

00:13:49.160 --> 00:13:50.040 line:80%
Men

00:13:50.190 --> 00:13:51.670 line:80%
use these

00:13:51.670 --> 00:13:53.040 line:80%
for hard labor.

00:13:53.120 --> 00:13:55.040 line:80%
Why would a girl need them?

00:13:55.120 --> 00:13:56.780 line:80%
You can't find them anywhere.

00:15:40.910 --> 00:15:47.520 line:80%
[Map of Great Yin]

00:15:51.120 --> 00:15:52.920 line:80%
Xie Zheng is alive?

00:15:53.240 --> 00:15:54.470 line:80%
Why didn't he die?

00:15:55.160 --> 00:15:56.420 line:80%
He did this on purpose.

00:15:56.950 --> 00:15:59.550 line:80%
He had to wait until the chaos erupted
before showing himself,

00:15:59.550 --> 00:16:01.590 line:80%
just to humiliate me!

00:16:02.470 --> 00:16:04.430 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an
has been hiding all this time.

00:16:04.430 --> 00:16:06.190 line:80%
He must be plotting something big.

00:16:06.190 --> 00:16:08.430 line:80%
The Xie Army and Yanzhou Army
are stubborn by nature

00:16:08.430 --> 00:16:10.000 line:80%
and refuse to follow our orders.

00:16:10.000 --> 00:16:11.760 line:80%
If you stay in the Northwest,

00:16:12.160 --> 00:16:13.830 line:80%
you'll be a sitting duck.

00:16:14.350 --> 00:16:17.550 line:80%
Returning to the Capital now
is the best course of action.

00:16:21.280 --> 00:16:21.810 line:80%
General!

00:16:21.920 --> 00:16:23.760 line:80%
Are you saying I'm afraid of him?

00:16:24.470 --> 00:16:26.040 line:80%
I'm staying right here.

00:16:26.590 --> 00:16:28.450 line:80%
I'd like to see what he can do to me.

00:16:29.070 --> 00:16:30.000 line:80%
I dare not.

00:16:32.310 --> 00:16:33.510 line:80%
Eldest Young Master.

00:16:34.070 --> 00:16:36.880 line:80%
Eldest Young Master,
don't let your temper get the best of you.

00:16:36.880 --> 00:16:40.520 line:80%
Now is not the time to confront
the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:16:41.470 --> 00:16:44.120 line:80%
We should first
take the news that he's still alive

00:16:44.120 --> 00:16:45.250 line:80%
back to the Capital.

00:16:45.400 --> 00:16:49.070 line:80%
We should focus on
the Prime Minister's great cause.

00:16:53.920 --> 00:16:55.450 line:80%
If it weren't for my father,

00:16:55.710 --> 00:16:58.040 line:80%
I wouldn't let that Xie Zheng
off the hook.

00:17:00.590 --> 00:17:02.760 line:80%
You are a filial son, Young Master.

00:17:03.070 --> 00:17:04.629 line:80%
You are a filial son.

00:17:05.540 --> 00:17:08.440 line:80%
[Chongde Hall]

00:17:09.310 --> 00:17:10.149 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:17:10.629 --> 00:17:12.070 line:80%
At court today,

00:17:12.070 --> 00:17:14.440 line:80%
there was much discussion
about the turmoil in the Northwest.

00:17:14.419 --> 00:17:17.940 line:80%
[Act with Caution]

00:17:14.909 --> 00:17:17.240 line:80%
I dared not claim credit publicly,

00:17:17.590 --> 00:17:19.869 line:80%
but there is one thing
I haven't reported to you.

00:17:17.980 --> 00:17:20.230 line:80%
[Speak with Caution]

00:17:21.800 --> 00:17:23.330 line:80%
Please speak, Grand Tutor.

00:17:23.350 --> 00:17:25.760 line:80%
For reasons unknown, Commissioner Wei

00:17:25.800 --> 00:17:27.350 line:80%
detained General He,

00:17:27.590 --> 00:17:30.390 line:80%
and almost caused civil unrest
in Qingping County.

00:17:30.390 --> 00:17:31.720 line:80%
Regarding this matter,

00:17:32.270 --> 00:17:35.550 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei, are you aware?

00:17:36.630 --> 00:17:38.760 line:80%
The matter involving General He

00:17:39.200 --> 00:17:41.720 line:80%
is a major military issue
on the front lines.

00:17:42.440 --> 00:17:44.680 line:80%
Wei Xuan's memorial of defense

00:17:44.800 --> 00:17:46.200 line:80%
has not yet arrived.

00:17:46.680 --> 00:17:48.800 line:80%
Grand Tutor, why are you so eager

00:17:48.800 --> 00:17:49.830 line:80%
to step forward

00:17:50.040 --> 00:17:53.040 line:80%
and intervene in this matter?
What is your intention?

00:17:53.070 --> 00:17:55.400 line:80%
Are you trying to make a big deal
out of this

00:17:55.550 --> 00:17:58.960 line:80%
or to frame someone?

00:17:59.440 --> 00:18:00.680 line:80%
I dare not.

00:18:01.590 --> 00:18:04.830 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei,
do not make false accusations.

00:18:07.680 --> 00:18:11.720 line:80%
Your Majesty,
I have something to congratulate you on.

00:18:12.350 --> 00:18:13.550 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an

00:18:14.150 --> 00:18:15.280 line:80%
is still alive.

00:18:16.830 --> 00:18:18.630 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an isn't dead?

00:18:20.970 --> 00:18:24.880 line:80%
[Think with Caution]

00:18:24.200 --> 00:18:26.930 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei,
congratulations to you too.

00:18:28.960 --> 00:18:32.760 line:80%
If the Marquis of Wu'an truly survived,

00:18:33.240 --> 00:18:35.440 line:80%
it will boost the army's morale

00:18:35.960 --> 00:18:39.200 line:80%
and strike fear into the rebels.

00:18:40.200 --> 00:18:40.910 line:80%
Yes, yes.

00:18:42.590 --> 00:18:44.590 line:80%
Congratulations, Prime Minister Wei.

00:18:44.590 --> 00:18:46.320 line:80%
Your top general has returned.

00:18:46.830 --> 00:18:48.720 line:80%
Truly a cause for celebration.

00:18:49.240 --> 00:18:49.970 line:80%
Yes, indeed.

00:18:55.310 --> 00:18:56.590 line:80%
Ministers,

00:18:56.910 --> 00:19:01.110 line:80%
this should be celebrated
by the whole country for 7...

00:19:02.830 --> 00:19:03.800 line:80%
5 days?

00:19:04.830 --> 00:19:06.200 line:80%
3 days would be the best.

00:19:08.000 --> 00:19:08.630 line:80%
Well...

00:19:09.280 --> 00:19:11.000 line:80%
how many days would be the best?

00:19:11.000 --> 00:19:12.680 line:80%
I second that.

00:19:12.800 --> 00:19:13.870 line:80%
We haven't even agreed
on the number of days yet.

00:19:13.870 --> 00:19:15.200 line:80%
What are you seconding?

00:19:15.550 --> 00:19:16.350 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:19:16.830 --> 00:19:19.280 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an is young
and his achievements are modest.

00:19:19.280 --> 00:19:20.800 line:80%
We dare not disturb the whole country.

00:19:20.800 --> 00:19:21.520 line:80%
I...

00:19:22.310 --> 00:19:24.070 line:80%
dare not accept such grand honors.

00:19:24.070 --> 00:19:25.200 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei,

00:19:25.520 --> 00:19:28.240 line:80%
leaving aside the Marquis of Wu'an's
outstanding military merits,

00:19:28.240 --> 00:19:29.870 line:80%
no matter how young he is,

00:19:30.200 --> 00:19:32.350 line:80%
he is His Majesty's Marquis of Wu'an,

00:19:32.680 --> 00:19:34.680 line:80%
not just your nephew.

00:19:35.480 --> 00:19:37.810 line:80%
Could it be that His Majesty's great favor

00:19:38.350 --> 00:19:42.070 line:80%
is less important than your modesty?

00:19:42.680 --> 00:19:43.910 line:80%
In that case,

00:19:44.800 --> 00:19:45.520 line:80%
alright.

00:19:46.110 --> 00:19:48.480 line:80%
On behalf of the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:19:49.310 --> 00:19:51.310 line:80%
I thank Your Majesty for your grace.

00:19:55.330 --> 00:19:59.320 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:20:01.760 --> 00:20:03.350 line:80%
Don't, Mom!

00:20:03.390 --> 00:20:04.760 line:80%
My son!

00:20:05.720 --> 00:20:07.070 line:80%
Don't go!

00:20:20.630 --> 00:20:22.280 line:80%
You must be very careful.

00:20:22.280 --> 00:20:24.280 line:80%
Don't try to be a hero on the battlefield.

00:20:24.280 --> 00:20:26.240 line:80%
You're old.
It's no shame to be afraid of death.

00:20:26.240 --> 00:20:27.300 line:80%
Do you understand?

00:20:28.310 --> 00:20:29.110 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:20:29.630 --> 00:20:32.430 line:80%
The God of War in Xigu Lane
is not to be trifled with.

00:20:34.310 --> 00:20:35.800 line:80%
Keep up!

00:20:36.390 --> 00:20:37.280 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:20:37.280 --> 00:20:38.000 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:20:38.040 --> 00:20:40.310 line:80%
Changyu has been in a bad mood these days.

00:20:40.310 --> 00:20:41.550 line:80%
So I didn't tell her.

00:20:41.550 --> 00:20:43.590 line:80%
I don't know where she is now.

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:46.260 line:80%
I certainly didn't dare tell Changning.

00:20:53.280 --> 00:20:54.880 line:80%
It's better they don't know.

00:20:55.480 --> 00:20:56.810 line:80%
It's actually the best.

00:21:04.590 --> 00:21:07.280 line:80%
When I seize some loot on the battlefield,

00:21:07.630 --> 00:21:10.630 line:80%
I'll come back
and trade it for a gold bracelet for you.

00:21:11.110 --> 00:21:12.200 line:80%
I don't want it!

00:21:13.150 --> 00:21:15.080 line:80%
I just want you to come back safely.

00:21:15.110 --> 00:21:16.240 line:80%
Our son is already gone.

00:21:16.240 --> 00:21:17.000 line:80%
Move it!

00:21:17.200 --> 00:21:19.040 line:80%
I can't lose you too!

00:21:19.480 --> 00:21:21.520 line:80%
You must come back safely! Do you hear me?

00:21:21.520 --> 00:21:22.350 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:21:22.720 --> 00:21:23.480 line:80%
I won't die!

00:21:24.680 --> 00:21:25.480 line:80%
I'm going!

00:21:27.350 --> 00:21:28.240 line:80%
Bye!

00:21:28.480 --> 00:21:29.800 line:80%
Come back safely!

00:21:32.960 --> 00:21:33.760 line:80%
Bro,

00:21:34.630 --> 00:21:36.230 line:80%
what about my little sister?

00:21:36.590 --> 00:21:38.720 line:80%
Who will take care of her after I leave?

00:21:38.760 --> 00:21:39.440 line:80%
Move!

00:21:39.870 --> 00:21:43.040 line:80%
Bro, we're not going to our deaths
this time, are we?

00:21:43.800 --> 00:21:45.000 line:80%
If I die,

00:21:45.350 --> 00:21:46.960 line:80%
I'll never see my mom again.

00:21:47.040 --> 00:21:49.150 line:80%
Pah! Don't say such unlucky things!

00:21:49.350 --> 00:21:52.040 line:80%
Child's words are meaningless.
Let the wind blow them away!

00:21:52.040 --> 00:21:53.590 line:80%
Go in good health

00:21:53.590 --> 00:21:55.000 line:80%
-and come back safely.
-Hurry!

00:21:55.000 --> 00:21:55.760 line:80%
Ma'am!

00:21:55.760 --> 00:21:56.550 line:80%
Move!

00:21:56.550 --> 00:21:58.110 line:80%
-Please send a word to Mrs. Fan.
-Get up!

00:21:58.110 --> 00:21:58.480 line:80%
Get up!

00:21:58.480 --> 00:22:00.070 line:80%
If she can take care of our family

00:22:00.070 --> 00:22:01.150 line:80%
and we make it back alive,

00:22:01.150 --> 00:22:02.720 line:80%
we'll work like slaves for her!

00:22:02.720 --> 00:22:03.630 line:80%
-I will!
-Go!

00:22:03.680 --> 00:22:04.910 line:80%
We'll work like slaves for her!

00:22:04.910 --> 00:22:06.040 line:80%
-I will.
-Get up!

00:22:06.280 --> 00:22:07.590 line:80%
Hurry up! Move!

00:22:15.240 --> 00:22:16.700 line:80%
-Don't pull me!
-Ms. Song!

00:22:17.280 --> 00:22:19.070 line:80%
-Ms. Song, please help me!
-Let go of me!

00:22:19.070 --> 00:22:20.200 line:80%
-Ms. Song!
-Let go!

00:22:20.200 --> 00:22:22.310 line:80%
-Let go of me!
-Ms. Song!

00:22:22.440 --> 00:22:23.910 line:80%
I'm begging you.

00:22:26.760 --> 00:22:28.000 line:80%
Ms. Song!

00:22:28.150 --> 00:22:30.080 line:80%
Please go to the County Magistrate

00:22:30.240 --> 00:22:32.840 line:80%
and beg for mercy for my grandson,
Kang Dan'er.

00:22:33.590 --> 00:22:36.000 line:80%
His father has already died in battle,

00:22:36.070 --> 00:22:38.070 line:80%
leaving behind this half-grown child.

00:22:38.070 --> 00:22:38.800 line:80%
Tell me,

00:22:39.440 --> 00:22:41.070 line:80%
if I lose this child too,

00:22:41.310 --> 00:22:43.200 line:80%
how am I supposed to live?

00:22:43.590 --> 00:22:44.680 line:80%
I'm begging you.

00:22:44.680 --> 00:22:45.910 line:80%
-Mrs. Kang, please get up.
-Ms. Song!

00:22:45.910 --> 00:22:47.000 line:80%
Please!

00:22:47.000 --> 00:22:49.000 line:80%
Get up before you speak. Come on.

00:22:50.630 --> 00:22:52.150 line:80%
Mrs. Kang,

00:22:52.630 --> 00:22:55.550 line:80%
serving the Imperial Court
is a man's duty.

00:22:55.830 --> 00:22:56.800 line:80%
Besides,

00:22:57.110 --> 00:22:59.550 line:80%
everyone has their own fate.

00:23:00.480 --> 00:23:03.440 line:80%
I think you should happily

00:23:03.440 --> 00:23:05.040 line:80%
let the child serve the country,

00:23:05.040 --> 00:23:08.370 line:80%
so that he won't let down
the Imperial Court's expectation.

00:23:09.040 --> 00:23:09.830 line:80%
Song!

00:23:11.040 --> 00:23:13.590 line:80%
Why didn't you send your Song Yan
to the front lines?

00:23:13.590 --> 00:23:15.440 line:80%
How can he dodge the draft?

00:23:15.440 --> 00:23:16.900 line:80%
How dare you, Granny Kang!

00:23:17.200 --> 00:23:18.110 line:80%
Let me tell you!

00:23:18.590 --> 00:23:20.240 line:80%
My son is a scholar!

00:23:20.110 --> 00:23:25.090 line:80%
[Lin'an]

00:23:20.240 --> 00:23:21.110 line:80%
Besides,

00:23:21.310 --> 00:23:24.310 line:80%
going to the Capital to study
is also serving the Imperial Court.

00:23:24.310 --> 00:23:25.370 line:80%
Do you understand?

00:23:26.920 --> 00:23:27.650 line:80%
Give it to me.

00:23:30.280 --> 00:23:31.280 line:80%
Forget it.

00:23:32.960 --> 00:23:36.310 line:80%
For the sake of our past friendship,

00:23:36.720 --> 00:23:37.520 line:80%
take these...

00:23:44.010 --> 00:23:46.040 line:80%
as a small token of my regard.

00:23:47.280 --> 00:23:48.340 line:80%
I won't see you off.

00:23:49.870 --> 00:23:50.720 line:80%
Go now.

00:24:13.280 --> 00:24:14.000 line:80%
Honey!

00:24:14.350 --> 00:24:14.760 line:80%
Hurry!

00:24:15.480 --> 00:24:18.040 line:80%
-Stop following us. Go back!
-Don't go!

00:24:23.390 --> 00:24:24.680 line:80%
Changyu!

00:24:25.310 --> 00:24:27.590 line:80%
Changyu, you're finally back.

00:24:28.630 --> 00:24:30.520 line:80%
If you had come back sooner,

00:24:30.800 --> 00:24:32.960 line:80%
you could have seen your uncle
one last time.

00:24:32.960 --> 00:24:35.280 line:80%
Pah! "One last time"? Pah!

00:24:35.720 --> 00:24:36.800 line:80%
What happened?

00:24:36.910 --> 00:24:37.720 line:80%
Jizhou is conscripting soldiers.

00:24:37.720 --> 00:24:39.350 line:80%
They took your uncle away.

00:24:39.390 --> 00:24:40.350 line:80%
They took Mr. Zhao away?

00:24:40.350 --> 00:24:40.800 line:80%
Yes.

00:24:40.800 --> 00:24:43.260 line:80%
Jin Yuanbao and his brothers
were all taken.

00:24:44.680 --> 00:24:45.680 line:80%
How could that be?

00:24:46.480 --> 00:24:47.340 line:80%
Is anyone here?

00:24:48.590 --> 00:24:49.310 line:80%
Is anyone here?

00:24:49.310 --> 00:24:50.240 line:80%
Yes!

00:24:51.040 --> 00:24:51.720 line:80%
We're here.

00:24:53.280 --> 00:24:54.480 line:80%
Which one of you is from the Fan family?

00:24:54.480 --> 00:24:55.350 line:80%
I am.

00:24:55.760 --> 00:24:56.910 line:80%
Are there any males in the family?

00:24:56.910 --> 00:24:57.720 line:80%
No.

00:24:58.110 --> 00:24:59.830 line:80%
This girl's husband
went on a long journey.

00:24:59.830 --> 00:25:01.560 line:80%
He won't be back for a year or so.

00:25:02.120 --> 00:25:03.650 line:80%
That same old excuse again.

00:25:03.800 --> 00:25:04.260 line:80%
Search!

00:25:04.310 --> 00:25:04.590 line:80%
Yes!

00:25:04.680 --> 00:25:04.960 line:80%
Hurry!

00:25:04.960 --> 00:25:05.290 line:80%
Wait!

00:25:09.390 --> 00:25:11.280 line:80%
This household
has already been conscripted.

00:25:11.280 --> 00:25:13.250 line:80%
Her husband must be among the group

00:25:13.480 --> 00:25:15.390 line:80%
we just caught on the way here.

00:25:16.590 --> 00:25:18.350 line:80%
My... my husband was taken?

00:25:18.720 --> 00:25:19.760 line:80%
Are you sure?

00:25:19.870 --> 00:25:22.760 line:80%
Is your husband named Yan Zheng?

00:25:28.000 --> 00:25:28.630 line:80%
Yes.

00:25:29.630 --> 00:25:30.960 line:80%
Where is he now?

00:25:31.440 --> 00:25:32.630 line:80%
Can I go see him?

00:25:33.200 --> 00:25:34.460 line:80%
He was caught outside,

00:25:34.520 --> 00:25:36.200 line:80%
so he surely didn't take anything
with him.

00:25:36.200 --> 00:25:38.440 line:80%
They have already set out
with the main force

00:25:38.440 --> 00:25:39.570 line:80%
heading to Lucheng.

00:25:39.630 --> 00:25:40.630 line:80%
If you go now,

00:25:40.720 --> 00:25:42.680 line:80%
I don't know if you can catch up.

00:25:44.280 --> 00:25:44.830 line:80%
Let's go.

00:25:57.040 --> 00:25:58.440 line:80%
Mrs.Zhao, I'm going out!

00:25:58.760 --> 00:26:00.630 line:80%
Changyu, where are you going?

00:26:06.150 --> 00:26:08.070 line:80%
Yanzheng, you must wait for me.

00:26:12.500 --> 00:26:21.160 line:80%
[Lin'an]

00:26:15.760 --> 00:26:16.800 line:80%
Go!

00:26:27.040 --> 00:26:27.800 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:26:29.070 --> 00:26:31.240 line:80%
The city is sealed.
Except for those on the conscription list,

00:26:31.240 --> 00:26:33.150 line:80%
no unauthorized persons may leave Lin'an.

00:26:33.150 --> 00:26:35.280 line:80%
Sir, I'll just deliver something
and come back.

00:26:35.280 --> 00:26:35.830 line:80%
No.

00:26:52.200 --> 00:26:53.660 line:80%
I didn't catch up with him.

00:26:58.340 --> 00:27:01.020 line:80%
Son, your father...

00:27:01.800 --> 00:27:04.460 line:80%
Honey, these are the clothes
Master got for you.

00:27:05.110 --> 00:27:06.200 line:80%
Take them.

00:27:07.440 --> 00:27:08.520 line:80%
M-Mr. Zhao?

00:27:09.720 --> 00:27:10.680 line:80%
Changyu?

00:27:14.910 --> 00:27:17.300 line:80%
I blame myself
for choosing the wrong trade.

00:27:17.300 --> 00:27:19.520 line:80%
I studied veterinary medicine
when I was young

00:27:19.520 --> 00:27:21.490 line:80%
and work as a carpenter now that I'm old.

00:27:21.490 --> 00:27:22.600 line:80%
The officer said

00:27:22.830 --> 00:27:23.960 line:80%
once I'm in the army,

00:27:23.990 --> 00:27:25.220 line:80%
I can be a vet,

00:27:25.350 --> 00:27:26.350 line:80%
a blacksmith,

00:27:26.910 --> 00:27:29.110 line:80%
and even repair siege weapons.

00:27:35.150 --> 00:27:35.830 line:80%
Mr. Zhao.

00:27:37.150 --> 00:27:38.550 line:80%
Take this horse with you.

00:27:40.800 --> 00:27:42.530 line:80%
Where did you get this horse?

00:27:42.560 --> 00:27:44.680 line:80%
I traded something for it
with Blacksmith Chen.

00:27:44.680 --> 00:27:46.930 line:80%
I heard horses are precious in the army.

00:27:47.310 --> 00:27:48.990 line:80%
If you take it to the camp,

00:27:49.150 --> 00:27:50.750 line:80%
they won't treat you poorly.

00:27:52.040 --> 00:27:52.960 line:80%
Good horse.

00:27:53.550 --> 00:27:54.590 line:80%
What a good horse.

00:27:56.310 --> 00:27:56.830 line:80%
Move.

00:27:57.000 --> 00:27:58.260 line:80%
I'm leaving, Changyu.

00:27:59.070 --> 00:28:00.000 line:80%
-Move!
-Move it!

00:28:02.040 --> 00:28:04.690 line:80%
Mr. Zhao, this is a package for Yan Zheng.

00:28:04.800 --> 00:28:05.910 line:80%
-I couldn't find him.
-Move it.

00:28:05.910 --> 00:28:07.210 line:80%
If you go to Lucheng

00:28:07.310 --> 00:28:08.910 line:80%
and see him, please give this to him.

00:28:08.910 --> 00:28:10.170 line:80%
Don't worry, Changyu.

00:28:10.390 --> 00:28:12.070 line:80%
As long as I'm alive,

00:28:12.150 --> 00:28:14.290 line:80%
I will definitely give it to him!

00:28:14.440 --> 00:28:17.370 line:80%
-Take good care of yourself!
-Don't worry, Changyu!

00:28:18.960 --> 00:28:20.680 line:80%
Take care!

00:28:20.680 --> 00:28:21.830 line:80%
Bye!

00:28:34.790 --> 00:28:38.020 line:80%
[Wei Residence]

00:28:52.680 --> 00:28:53.280 line:80%
Father.

00:28:54.350 --> 00:28:55.750 line:80%
Xie Zheng is still alive.

00:28:56.720 --> 00:28:59.720 line:80%
I came back specifically
to congratulate you.

00:29:05.720 --> 00:29:09.070 line:80%
As a border commander,
you repeatedly ignored orders,

00:29:09.070 --> 00:29:10.650 line:80%
forcing civilians into conscription

00:29:10.650 --> 00:29:13.150 line:80%
and launching a direct assault
on Chongzhou—

00:29:13.150 --> 00:29:15.010 line:80%
this is a serious crime.

00:29:15.720 --> 00:29:16.440 line:80%
You...

00:29:17.150 --> 00:29:19.280 line:80%
should just wait for your punishment.

00:29:19.280 --> 00:29:20.610 line:80%
I am not afraid of death.

00:29:21.350 --> 00:29:23.800 line:80%
I rushed home to report to you

00:29:24.480 --> 00:29:26.140 line:80%
that Xie Zheng and He Jingyuan

00:29:26.200 --> 00:29:27.480 line:80%
are colluding.

00:29:28.680 --> 00:29:29.630 line:80%
Colluding?

00:29:31.950 --> 00:29:33.480 line:80%
One is my nephew,

00:29:33.800 --> 00:29:35.310 line:80%
and the other is my subordinate.

00:29:35.310 --> 00:29:37.110 line:80%
How can you call it "collusion"?

00:29:37.520 --> 00:29:38.440 line:80%
You...

00:29:38.460 --> 00:29:41.070 line:80%
are just afraid that after Xie Zheng
returns to Yanzhou,

00:29:41.070 --> 00:29:43.670 line:80%
he will seek revenge for the arrow
you shot him,

00:29:44.390 --> 00:29:46.250 line:80%
so you fled back here, didn't you?

00:29:50.200 --> 00:29:51.280 line:80%
Father, even now,

00:29:51.280 --> 00:29:54.080 line:80%
you still side with that ingrate
who betrayed you?

00:29:54.310 --> 00:29:56.840 line:80%
I only regret
that arrow didn't take his life.

00:29:57.040 --> 00:29:57.760 line:80%
I merely did what you wanted to do

00:29:57.760 --> 00:29:59.870 line:80%
but could not bear to do yourself.

00:30:01.910 --> 00:30:03.520 line:80%
If he truly kills me,

00:30:04.830 --> 00:30:06.560 line:80%
will that make you any happier?

00:30:09.390 --> 00:30:10.200 line:80%
Insolence!

00:30:10.480 --> 00:30:13.940 line:80%
You contradicted the Prime Minister.
This is a grave mistake!

00:30:16.710 --> 00:30:17.840 line:80%
The Prime Minister?

00:30:21.720 --> 00:30:23.000 line:80%
He is your husband,

00:30:23.760 --> 00:30:26.620 line:80%
yet you only ever address him
by his official title.

00:30:26.720 --> 00:30:28.580 line:80%
It's normal if you are estranged,

00:30:28.720 --> 00:30:30.910 line:80%
yet you hold him in higher regard
than anyone,

00:30:30.910 --> 00:30:32.110 line:80%
treat Xie Zheng like your own child,

00:30:32.110 --> 00:30:34.040 line:80%
and allow Father to treat me
as if I were nothing.

00:30:34.040 --> 00:30:35.590 line:80%
Why is that?

00:30:38.760 --> 00:30:40.480 line:80%
Just remember one thing—

00:30:41.480 --> 00:30:43.080 line:80%
without the Prime Minister,

00:30:43.550 --> 00:30:45.680 line:80%
you wouldn't have what you have today.

00:30:51.480 --> 00:30:52.830 line:80%
If I were Nezha,

00:30:54.480 --> 00:30:57.140 line:80%
I'd rather give my own flesh
to repay my parents.

00:30:58.590 --> 00:30:59.390 line:80%
Xuan!

00:31:15.440 --> 00:31:16.590 line:80%
This child was rude

00:31:16.830 --> 00:31:18.150 line:80%
and offended you.

00:31:18.480 --> 00:31:20.630 line:80%
Please take care of your health

00:31:21.240 --> 00:31:24.870 line:80%
and do not let this anger harm you.

00:31:25.210 --> 00:31:26.040 line:80%
It's alright.

00:31:30.830 --> 00:31:32.350 line:80%
Zheng is still alive.

00:31:33.480 --> 00:31:34.830 line:80%
Zheng is still alive?

00:31:35.940 --> 00:31:37.440 line:80%
Zheng is still alive...

00:31:38.140 --> 00:31:39.700 line:80%
Thank God.

00:31:40.110 --> 00:31:42.310 line:80%
You are truly blessed, Prime Minister.

00:31:43.040 --> 00:31:44.790 line:80%
You finally have a successor.

00:31:50.650 --> 00:31:54.200 line:80%
[Wei Residence]

00:31:53.240 --> 00:31:55.520 line:80%
Prime Minister, Xie Zheng is not dead.

00:31:55.830 --> 00:31:58.000 line:80%
The situation in the Northwest may change.

00:31:58.000 --> 00:31:59.310 line:80%
I await your orders.

00:31:59.870 --> 00:32:01.680 line:80%
Go to the Northwest immediately

00:32:02.280 --> 00:32:03.240 line:80%
and find out

00:32:03.240 --> 00:32:05.680 line:80%
what Xie Zheng's attitude is now.

00:32:06.480 --> 00:32:07.870 line:80%
And that He Jingyuan—

00:32:08.240 --> 00:32:10.440 line:80%
he knew Xie Zheng was alive

00:32:10.910 --> 00:32:12.200 line:80%
but kept it a secret

00:32:12.550 --> 00:32:13.830 line:80%
and even joined forces with him.

00:32:13.830 --> 00:32:15.720 line:80%
Why did he do that?

00:32:16.280 --> 00:32:16.870 line:80%
Yes.

00:32:17.440 --> 00:32:19.390 line:80%
Lord Changxin's plan to use refugees

00:32:19.390 --> 00:32:20.870 line:80%
to break through Jizhou failed.

00:32:20.870 --> 00:32:22.110 line:80%
He will surely strike back.

00:32:22.110 --> 00:32:24.640 line:80%
Now that He Jingyuan
is stationed in Lucheng,

00:32:25.340 --> 00:32:27.200 line:80%
regarding the affairs of Jizhou,

00:32:27.630 --> 00:32:29.430 line:80%
who will be sent to take command?

00:32:29.830 --> 00:32:31.070 line:80%
Li Huai'an?

00:32:31.910 --> 00:32:33.910 line:80%
If I'm not mistaken,

00:32:34.280 --> 00:32:36.240 line:80%
He Jingyuan's memorial of petition

00:32:36.240 --> 00:32:38.280 line:80%
is already on its way.

00:32:39.870 --> 00:32:43.480 line:80%
Could it be that the relationship between
Li Huai'an and He Jingyuan

00:32:43.480 --> 00:32:45.630 line:80%
was part of Grand Tutor Li's plan

00:32:45.760 --> 00:32:46.800 line:80%
over 10 years ago?

00:32:46.960 --> 00:32:49.550 line:80%
It was just a matter
of seizing the opportunity

00:32:49.550 --> 00:32:51.200 line:80%
and going with the flow.

00:32:51.390 --> 00:32:52.920 line:80%
Back in the Eastern Palace,

00:32:53.480 --> 00:32:55.680 line:80%
in civil affairs there were me
and Grand Tutor Tao,

00:32:55.680 --> 00:32:59.520 line:80%
and in military matters there were
Xie Linshan and General Meng.

00:33:00.040 --> 00:33:03.110 line:80%
Li Xing was nothing but a clown.

00:33:03.200 --> 00:33:05.800 line:80%
Do you think He Jingyuan
will really betray you

00:33:06.760 --> 00:33:08.280 line:80%
and collude with the Li family?

00:33:08.280 --> 00:33:09.280 line:80%
Not necessarily.

00:33:09.910 --> 00:33:12.590 line:80%
He Jingyuan values his promises.

00:33:13.390 --> 00:33:15.960 line:80%
It won't be easy for the Li family

00:33:16.350 --> 00:33:17.680 line:80%
to interfere in Jizhou.

00:33:18.000 --> 00:33:19.760 line:80%
Go to the Northwest immediately

00:33:19.760 --> 00:33:21.420 line:80%
and gather more information.

00:33:22.000 --> 00:33:22.550 line:80%
Yes.

00:33:26.640 --> 00:33:28.230 line:80%
It's been 17 years.

00:33:29.680 --> 00:33:32.630 line:80%
Is it time to make a decision again?

00:33:38.800 --> 00:33:42.850 line:80%
♪ The world is vast ♪

00:33:44.190 --> 00:33:50.150 line:80%
♪ The storm is rising ♪

00:33:46.000 --> 00:33:49.050 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an! Marquis of Wu'an!

00:33:49.080 --> 00:33:52.320 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an! Marquis of Wu'an!

00:33:51.860 --> 00:33:56.000 line:80%
♪ Day and night ♪

00:33:52.340 --> 00:33:55.700 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an! Marquis of Wu'an!

00:33:55.730 --> 00:33:58.940 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an! Marquis of Wu'an!

00:33:57.610 --> 00:34:00.830 line:80%
♪ We strive to save the world ♪

00:33:58.960 --> 00:34:02.180 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an! Marquis of Wu'an!

00:34:02.200 --> 00:34:05.540 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an! Marquis of Wu'an!

00:34:04.860 --> 00:34:09.120 line:80%
♪ All people ♪

00:34:05.560 --> 00:34:08.660 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an! Marquis of Wu'an!

00:34:08.689 --> 00:34:11.860 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an! Marquis of Wu'an!

00:34:10.340 --> 00:34:15.870 line:80%
♪ Are part of the past ♪

00:34:11.200 --> 00:34:14.590 line:80%
[Marquis of Wu'an]

00:34:11.880 --> 00:34:14.800 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an! Marquis of Wu'an!

00:34:18.269 --> 00:34:22.870 line:80%
♪ What's the date today? ♪

00:34:23.390 --> 00:34:24.800 line:80%
Your Lordship, the wound on your face…

00:34:23.670 --> 00:34:31.370 line:80%
♪ How lamentable ♪

00:34:24.990 --> 00:34:25.950 line:80%
-Don't ask what you shouldn't ask.
-Your wound...

00:34:25.950 --> 00:34:27.680 line:80%
-Did Mrs. Fan hit you?
-Get out!

00:34:28.470 --> 00:34:29.670 line:80%
You guys go out first.

00:34:29.950 --> 00:34:30.470 line:80%
Yes.

00:34:30.470 --> 00:34:31.080 line:80%
Did you get dumped?

00:34:31.080 --> 00:34:32.280 line:80%
-Tell me...
-You too.

00:34:33.120 --> 00:34:34.240 line:80%
Me too?

00:34:34.350 --> 00:34:35.479 line:80%
Xie Jiuheng, you...

00:34:35.720 --> 00:34:36.680 line:80%
I refuse!

00:34:40.160 --> 00:34:41.910 line:80%
Your Lordship, there's a letter
from the spy in the Capital,

00:34:41.910 --> 00:34:44.640 line:80%
saying Wei Sheng
is already on his way to the camp.

00:34:46.950 --> 00:34:49.280 line:80%
It seems he already knows I'm still alive.

00:34:50.600 --> 00:34:52.200 line:80%
It was sooner than expected.

00:34:52.760 --> 00:34:55.090 line:80%
Lord Changxin's army has left Chongzhou.

00:34:55.430 --> 00:34:57.640 line:80%
Their next stop will surely be Lucheng.

00:34:58.950 --> 00:35:01.750 line:80%
He Jingyuan is already ordering
reinforcements.

00:35:03.390 --> 00:35:05.280 line:80%
The ones Lord Changxin trusts most

00:35:05.280 --> 00:35:06.600 line:80%
are the Sui brothers,

00:35:06.950 --> 00:35:08.680 line:80%
Sui Yuanhuai and Sui Yuanqing.

00:35:08.720 --> 00:35:11.380 line:80%
If the Yanzhou army
wants to reinforce Lucheng,

00:35:12.240 --> 00:35:13.910 line:80%
the best place to deploy troops

00:35:13.910 --> 00:35:18.140 line:80%
[Baxia]

00:35:15.510 --> 00:35:16.470 line:80%
is Baxia.

00:35:19.240 --> 00:35:20.030 line:80%
Baxia?

00:35:20.600 --> 00:35:22.530 line:80%
Were you really beaten by Mrs. Fan?

00:35:23.280 --> 00:35:24.680 line:80%
Ouch, ouch, ouch!

00:35:27.030 --> 00:35:27.640 line:80%
Come.

00:35:38.310 --> 00:35:38.950 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao.

00:35:38.990 --> 00:35:40.560 line:80%
Manager Yu, Bao'er.

00:35:41.280 --> 00:35:43.680 line:80%
I thought it looked like you,
and it really is you.

00:35:43.680 --> 00:35:44.800 line:80%
Long time no see.

00:35:45.030 --> 00:35:46.360 line:80%
Come on. Come in and sit.

00:35:46.760 --> 00:35:47.960 line:80%
Thank you, Mrs. Zhao.

00:35:48.870 --> 00:35:50.350 line:80%
I'm here to see Changyu.

00:35:50.640 --> 00:35:51.560 line:80%
Is she home?

00:35:51.680 --> 00:35:54.470 line:80%
Changyu took Changning to see Mr. Jin
and the others.

00:35:54.470 --> 00:35:56.560 line:80%
She went to deliver some food
to their families.

00:35:56.560 --> 00:35:57.690 line:80%
She'll be back soon.

00:35:58.560 --> 00:35:59.430 line:80%
Here she is.

00:36:00.600 --> 00:36:02.600 line:80%
Qianqian, what brings you here?

00:36:02.600 --> 00:36:03.800 line:80%
-Changning.
-Changyu.

00:36:03.800 --> 00:36:04.950 line:80%
Go inside and sit. It's so cold out here.

00:36:04.950 --> 00:36:06.310 line:80%
Come on. Come in and sit.

00:36:06.390 --> 00:36:06.910 line:80%
Come.

00:36:06.910 --> 00:36:07.280 line:80%
Let's go.

00:36:07.280 --> 00:36:09.510 line:80%
You two haven't seen each other
for a long time, right?

00:36:09.510 --> 00:36:10.240 line:80%
Go play.

00:36:10.310 --> 00:36:11.800 line:80%
-Come on.
-I won't go in.

00:36:13.680 --> 00:36:15.210 line:80%
I came to say goodbye to you.

00:36:15.600 --> 00:36:16.720 line:80%
We are leaving.

00:36:18.800 --> 00:36:19.600 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:36:20.310 --> 00:36:22.040 line:80%
Let's sit there and talk. Come.

00:36:25.470 --> 00:36:26.600 line:80%
Here, have some tea.

00:36:26.800 --> 00:36:28.000 line:80%
Thank you, Mrs. Zhao.

00:36:30.990 --> 00:36:33.990 line:80%
A few days ago, the body
of my managing lady

00:36:34.030 --> 00:36:35.470 line:80%
was found in the snow.

00:36:36.310 --> 00:36:37.830 line:80%
I reported it to the authorities.

00:36:37.830 --> 00:36:40.430 line:80%
They said she might have
encountered bandits.

00:36:44.240 --> 00:36:46.300 line:80%
Did you notice anything suspicious?

00:36:47.830 --> 00:36:48.680 line:80%
I don't know.

00:36:49.680 --> 00:36:50.720 line:80%
But deep down,

00:36:51.280 --> 00:36:53.340 line:80%
I always feel a vague sense of unease.

00:36:53.470 --> 00:36:55.120 line:80%
Jizhou is in chaos now.

00:36:55.720 --> 00:36:57.650 line:80%
I don't know if Lucheng can be held.

00:36:57.950 --> 00:37:00.610 line:80%
Seeing that other merchants
have already left,

00:37:00.990 --> 00:37:02.600 line:80%
I plan to go to Jiangnan
to take refuge too.

00:37:02.600 --> 00:37:05.080 line:80%
I've almost finished packing.

00:37:05.640 --> 00:37:07.100 line:80%
I plan to set off tomorrow.

00:37:09.030 --> 00:37:11.680 line:80%
I heard your husband was also conscripted.

00:37:12.390 --> 00:37:13.910 line:80%
Why don't you bring Changning along,

00:37:13.910 --> 00:37:15.370 line:80%
and we can leave together?

00:37:22.080 --> 00:37:23.680 line:80%
Thank you for your kindness,

00:37:23.870 --> 00:37:24.830 line:80%
but I won't go.

00:37:26.390 --> 00:37:28.560 line:80%
Yan Zheng was conscripted to Lucheng.

00:37:29.640 --> 00:37:31.370 line:80%
I need to wait for him in Lin'an.

00:37:34.030 --> 00:37:36.430 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao is also waiting here
for Mr. Zhao.

00:37:37.280 --> 00:37:38.760 line:80%
She only has me left.

00:37:39.310 --> 00:37:41.640 line:80%
I can't leave her alone
at a time like this.

00:37:45.760 --> 00:37:47.290 line:80%
Take good care of yourself.

00:37:47.800 --> 00:37:48.600 line:80%
Safe travels.

00:37:56.500 --> 00:38:01.870 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:38:01.200 --> 00:38:02.350 line:80%
Here, this is for you.

00:38:02.350 --> 00:38:02.990 line:80%
No.

00:38:03.800 --> 00:38:05.000 line:80%
This is too precious.

00:38:06.200 --> 00:38:07.510 line:80%
Let Changning keep it.

00:38:08.030 --> 00:38:09.760 line:80%
It's Bao'er's favorite thing.

00:38:10.080 --> 00:38:13.240 line:80%
We don't know when we'll meet again.

00:38:23.120 --> 00:38:25.430 line:80%
But I have nothing to give you.

00:38:26.910 --> 00:38:27.720 line:80%
I want this.

00:38:28.560 --> 00:38:32.120 line:80%
Mr. Zhao wove this grasshopper for me
before he left.

00:38:32.430 --> 00:38:34.090 line:80%
Mr. Zhao went to join the army.

00:38:34.240 --> 00:38:36.720 line:80%
No one will weave grasshoppers for me
anymore.

00:38:36.720 --> 00:38:38.280 line:80%
You must keep it safe.

00:38:39.120 --> 00:38:40.980 line:80%
If you don't want it in the future,

00:38:41.030 --> 00:38:44.230 line:80%
bring the grasshopper back
to exchange for your pendant.

00:38:49.870 --> 00:38:51.160 line:80%
I will keep it safe.

00:38:54.310 --> 00:38:56.080 line:80%
I carry this with me all the time.

00:38:56.080 --> 00:38:57.210 line:80%
I'll leave it to you.

00:38:58.910 --> 00:39:00.310 line:80%
There's knockout powder inside.

00:39:00.310 --> 00:39:02.910 line:80%
Throw it when necessary.
It can save your life.

00:39:10.560 --> 00:39:11.620 line:80%
We'll be going now.

00:39:13.200 --> 00:39:13.830 line:80%
Take care.

00:39:15.430 --> 00:39:16.430 line:80%
Bao'er, let's go.

00:39:31.760 --> 00:39:33.120 line:80%
The falcon is gone.

00:39:33.800 --> 00:39:35.030 line:80%
Zheng is gone.

00:39:36.120 --> 00:39:37.160 line:80%
Mr. Zhao is gone.

00:39:38.200 --> 00:39:39.430 line:80%
Bao'er is gone too.

00:39:39.720 --> 00:39:41.120 line:80%
I miss them.

00:39:41.310 --> 00:39:43.510 line:80%
You still have me and Mrs. Zhao with you.

00:39:44.390 --> 00:39:45.600 line:80%
When the war is over,

00:39:46.080 --> 00:39:47.410 line:80%
they will all come back.

00:40:04.030 --> 00:40:06.760 line:80%
Master, the Old Prince's messenger
has arrived.

00:40:08.030 --> 00:40:10.430 line:80%
Here's an urgent letter from His Highness.

00:40:25.870 --> 00:40:27.130 line:80%
Thank you, messenger.

00:40:28.710 --> 00:40:29.610 line:80%
[Urgent Letter]

00:40:31.150 --> 00:40:33.970 line:80%
[We achieved nothing in Chongzhou]

00:40:32.950 --> 00:40:35.720 line:80%
Your “clever plan” caused
the provisions in Jizhou to be hijacked.

00:40:35.720 --> 00:40:37.160 line:80%
We achieved nothing.

00:40:37.240 --> 00:40:39.030 line:80%
Now the great battle of Lucheng
is imminent.

00:40:39.030 --> 00:40:40.630 line:80%
Come back here immediately!

00:40:43.350 --> 00:40:45.150 line:80%
His Highness is in a fit of anger.

00:40:45.560 --> 00:40:48.510 line:80%
Eldest Young Master,
you'd better set off immediately

00:40:48.510 --> 00:40:50.680 line:80%
and go to Lucheng to provide support.

00:40:57.120 --> 00:40:57.720 line:80%
I will.

00:40:57.760 --> 00:40:58.390 line:80%
I will.

00:41:00.120 --> 00:41:02.430 line:80%
Has the Heir Apparent been found?

00:41:03.390 --> 00:41:04.280 line:80%
Not yet.

00:41:05.830 --> 00:41:06.640 line:80%
See you.

00:41:35.990 --> 00:41:38.870 line:80%
Master,
he was Lord Changxin's trusted aide.

00:41:39.350 --> 00:41:41.200 line:80%
How are we going to explain this later?

00:41:41.200 --> 00:41:42.870 line:80%
This person was never here.

00:41:43.030 --> 00:41:44.560 line:80%
There is no need to explain.

00:41:45.510 --> 00:41:47.510 line:80%
Get ready. We're leaving tomorrow.

00:41:47.990 --> 00:41:49.320 line:80%
Are we going to Lucheng?

00:41:51.910 --> 00:41:53.370 line:80%
We're going to find her...

00:41:53.640 --> 00:41:55.040 line:80%
and that little bastard.

00:41:55.760 --> 00:41:59.600 line:80%
Run! The bandits are here! Help!

00:42:04.160 --> 00:42:05.430 line:80%
Over here!

00:42:26.900 --> 00:42:27.940 line:80%
You are...